Transworld Airlines Inc plans to refilean application Monday with the Department of Transportation forapproval to acquire USAir Group &lt;U>.    The DOT late today dismissed TWA's application to acquireUSAir.    "When the DOT opens for business on Monday morning, we willbe refiling a perfected and completed section 408 application,"said TWA general counsel Mark Buckstein.    Buckstein said the DOT ruled the application, which wasfiled Wednesday, was incomplete. He said he did not yet knowwhy the agency objected. Reuter&#3;